          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">BJJ Belt Guide</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Complete belt system breakdown</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/mma-gym-software/" class="card p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
